name: Krampus: The Yule Lord
description: “Your dreams are your spirit, your soul and without them your are dead. You must guard your dreams always. Always. Lest someone steal them away from you. I know what it is to have your dreams stolen. I know what it is to be dead. Guard your dreams. Always guard your dreams.” ― Brom, Krampus: The Yule Lord (mp4, 1084x1084, 0:12, music by @astralechoe)
